<solution>
<p><ul><li>7.5001597664158</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={1100}{e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{6174}={1100}{e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{6174}}{{1100}}={e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{6174}}{{1100}}\right)}}}={0.23}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{6174}}{{1100}}\right)}}}}{{0.23}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={7.5001597664158}</m></p>
</solution>
